@node Main

   @{b}MUI Spell 1.2@{ub}
   @{i}© Dirk Holtwick, 1995-1996@{ui}

   MUISpell is a GUI for the great AlphaSpell package that was  written  by
   Fergus Duniho in 1995. AlphaSpell is SHAREWARE. Please register it.

   If you came across this and don't have AlphaSpell, you can  find  it  on
   the Aminet  as  text/edit/ASpell.lha.  Make  sure  that  you  are  using
   AlphaSpell 6.0, since that is the latest  version.  If  you  don't  have
   Internet access, try a local Amiga BBS, or ask your  Sysop  to  make  it
   available for you.


   @{"  " link "Use" 0} How to use

   @{"  " link "COPYING/Main" 0} License
